                <note rend="inline" type="source">875.01/191: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Child</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-04-24T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 24, 1922—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>52. Your confidential despatch No. 251 April 3. Report by telegraph countries
                    which have recognized Albania, whether <hi rend="italic">de facto</hi> or <hi
                        rend="italic">de jure</hi> recognition has been given and the exact
                    designation of representatives who have been sent.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
